Package: opencode-traffic-light
Version: 0.5.0
Architecture: amd64
Maintainer: CuriousTank
Depends: libx11-6, libxcb1, libxi6, libxext6, libxdo3, libgtk-3-0, libappindicator3-1
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Description: Floating always-on-top traffic light monitor for opencode task status
 A small Rust/egui desktop widget that shows red/yellow/green bulbs
 reflecting the real-time status of opencode sessions (running/input/done).
 Includes the opencode status-pusher plugin.
